Generate the Tuning Grid for Tuning Hyperparameters

get_tuning_grid.Rd

Generate the Tuning Grid for Tuning Hyperparameters

get_tuning_grid(hyperparams_list, method)

Arguments

hyperparams_list

named list of lists of hyperparameters
method

ML method ("regLogistic", "svmRadial", "rpart2", "rf", "xgbTree")

Value

The tuning grid

Examples

get_tuning_grid(default_hyperparams, "regLogistic")
